'''Fengite''' is a [[Transparency and translucency|translucent]] sheet of [[marble]] or [[alabaster]] used during the [[Early Middle Ages]] for [[window]]s instead of [[glass]].<ref>[https://link.springer.com/referenceworkentry/10.1007%2F978-3-642-41714-6_60522 Dictionary Geotechnical Engineering, "fengite". Springer 2014]</ref><ref>[http://machaut.uchicago.edu/?resource=Webster's&word=Fengite&use1913=on Websters 1913 dictionary]</ref>

