The [[Bayer designation]] '''Omicron Cancri''' (ο Cnc / ο Cancri) is shared by two [[star]]s, in the [[constellation]] [[Cancer (constellation)|Cancer]]: * [[Omicron1 Cancri|ο¹ Cancri]] * [[Omicron2 Cancri|ο² Cancri]] They are separated by 0.27° on the sky. With a physical separation of {{Convert|0.2163|pc|ly}}, the stars most likely form a co-moving pair.<ref name=Shaya2011/>
